OL,3,CTommy Fury admits to downing '20 shots
OL,4,Ca night' before Molly-Mae split
OL,6,FTommy Fury has admitted he was downing
OL,7,F"20 shots a night" and drinking to get
OL,8,F"blackout drunk" ahead of his split
OL,9,Fwith Molly-Mae Hague.
OL,11,FThe boxer, 26, met Hague on ITV dating
OL,12,Fshow Love Island in 2019 and the pair
OL,13,Fhave a daughter, Bambi.
OL,15,FThe news of their split in August
OL,16,F2024, just more than a year after
OL,17,Ftheir engagement, sparked shock and
OL,18,Fspeculation he had been unfaithful.
