OL,3,CTommy Fury admits to downing '20 shots
OL,4,Ca night' before Molly-Mae split
OL,6,FFury, the half-brother of boxer Tyson,
OL,7,Fdenies the rumours in his new BBC
OL,8,FThree docu-series Tommy: The Good, The
OL,9,FBad, The Fury, saying he started
OL,10,Fdrinking heavily after injuring his
OL,11,Fhand.
OL,13,FHe said: "The reason for our ending
OL,14,Fthe relationship was alcohol."
OL,16,FHe added: "I couldn't train, box, lift
OL,17,Fweights, that was all gone.
OL,19,F"My right hand was messed up, I was in
OL,20,Fdire pain, it's just what happens over
OL,21,Fyears of impact on the hand.
