OL,6,F"I had lost my entire identity, lost
OL,7,Fmy life."
OL,9,FIn the first episode of the show,
OL,10,FFury's father John says he urged Hague
OL,11,Fto leave his son, saying: "I knew from
OL,12,Fdealing with Tyson, when the drinking
OL,13,Fstarted to come into play I thought
OL,14,F'Not again'.
OL,16,F"I did say to Molly, because she came
OL,17,Fto me, what you're best off doing with
OL,18,Fhim, Molly, is walking away, because
OL,19,Fif he's not going to change himself,
OL,20,Fhe doesn't think that much of you."
