OL,6,FRevealing how much he was drinking at
OL,7,Fthe time, Fury said: "I hold my hands
OL,8,Fup, drink got hold of me ` 20 shots a
OL,9,Fnight, 20 beers.
OL,11,F"Every day I would have a drink and I
OL,12,Fwould drink to get blackout drunk, and
OL,13,Fthat is what led to me not being the
OL,14,Fright partner to Molly."
