OL,3,CTommy Fury admits to downing '20 shots
OL,4,Ca night' before Molly-Mae split
OL,6,FDiscussing how it impacted him to be
OL,7,Funable to fight, he said: "The only
OL,8,Fthing that made me feel like I was
OL,9,Fback in that moment of thousands of
OL,10,Ffans again was picking up and having a
OL,11,Fdrink, but having a drink was what
OL,12,Fcost me my entire family.
OL,14,F"The reason why everything went to
OL,15,Fs**t, I went through the worst year of
OL,16,Fmy life, I went through a crisis, was
OL,17,Fbecause I couldn't fight."
OL,19,FHe admitted he was drunk when Hague
OL,20,Feventually walked out, taking their
OL,21,Fdaughter with her.
